    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Finely chop your <strong>chives</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> lemon[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p>",
