    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced shallot</strong> to a large bowl with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon wedges </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and set aside for 1-2 min</p><p>After 1-2 min,<strong> </strong>add your<strong> mayo</strong> to the bowl and stir it all together – this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
