    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to cover the base of the pan) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> smoky breaded tofu</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until browned – this is your <strong>tofu schnitzel</strong></p>",
