      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tofu is cooking, add your <strong>trimmed</strong> <strong>green beans</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them) and bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p><p>Once the potatoes are done, add the <strong>crispy potatoes </strong>and<strong> chopped chives</strong> to the <strong>quick-pickled shallot mayo </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled potato salad</strong></p>",
