    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tofu schnitzel </strong>with the <strong>quick-pickled potato salad</strong> and <strong>cooked green beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>remaining lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
